# .did files are generated by Basilisk builds but we track the source ones
# so that `dfx generate` works in CI without a full Basilisk rebuild.
# .dfx/ is already ignored above, so only src/**/*.did matters.
*.did
!src/**/*.did
*temp
*.pem
!src/declarations/
*.log
integration-test-logs/
playwright-report
test-results

# Extension deployment artifacts (source code is in extensions/)
